=head2 navigator

 navigator {topic_ids} {num} {offset}

Generates navigation links (to previous and next
stories in the C<topic_ids> set). Used for paging
in the C<INDEX> and C<TOPIC> templates.

=cut
<span class = 'prev'>{-if|$2|<a href='{-url|{-var|t|INDEX}|topic|$0|offset|{-sub|$2|$1}}'>&lt;&lt;</a>}</span>
&nbsp;
<span class = 'next'>{-if|{-stories_by_date|{-or|$0|{-cfg_index_topics}}|$1|{-add|$2|$1}}|<a href='{-url|{-var|t|INDEX}|topic|$0|offset|{-add|$2|$1}}'>&gt;&gt;</a>}</span>
